Because the gifts are sent out according to tenure and anniversary we can expect approx 75 gifts over a range of 12 months, so this is the top end number we are looking at but this may go up or down. I am keen to make this an impactful gift for the budget that we have as this is an opportunity for our new colleagues to feel they have made a great recruitment choice in joining SiteMinder and I would prefer these to be alcohol free, but open to suggestions on token gifts containing alcohol. We are proposing that these gifts would need shipping to mainland Europe and the UK, (Spain, Italy, Germany, France) etc.  We also have site operations in Thailand, US and Australia, but I know from other suppliers and speaking to yourselves as well that the cost may be prohibitive. I would like to be able to understand what can be acheived with the budget we have including any associated costs fo shipping and of course what you are able to accomodate for a bulk order.  I would ideally like an early overview today of what this might look like if possible? Kind regards Marie-Anne Varela
